,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T12:55:05.000Z","msg":"坤狗同佢班打手肯收皮未<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日做柒事想搏反彈<br />\n愈做愈乞人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3003cb9c8b28d2cb3f75f134dbe2091f102b03c9","tid":837562,"uid":132587,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T12:57:06.000Z","msg":"吳業坤博出位d招用得七七八八<br />\n你氣數已盡架啦<br />\n仲以為好似以前 專登打錯隻字就有人討論咩<br />\n宜家你話你鐘意飽姐都無人理架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8580de1b828750ce3aff6a4f6105007768f266","tid":837562,"uid":81183,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T12:59:26.000Z","msg":"家燕後面有唔加番個姐<br />\n佢係咪咁唔識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算家燕姐係咁多個阿姐入面最nice,  都咁話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢會唔會on9 到直接叫dodo<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc09a8442168bd62fc07d879c91ef69f097454d4","tid":837562,"uid":75832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:00:22.000Z","msg":"咪撚扮晒講笑懶幽默搏宣傳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56a51a87d82f5414b44643c84731e6e551a7cf6","tid":837562,"uid":63641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:00:50.000Z","msg":"Nancy 都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82cda1f21eee790e8dccea2168ce5e7882303a22","tid":837562,"uid":16624,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:01:20.000Z","msg":"問吓ig上面班中小學生，個個都覺得佢紅啦<br />\n使鬼理辣殺討論區講乜"},{"pid":"fddb008af9ad59eb2bcc7bd3da8d8deed3044d78","tid":837562,"uid":137831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:33:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【我的家燕寶寶】王梓軒爆吳業坤專影薛家燕唇印</span><br />\n現年27歲的歌手吳業坤最近再爆新「戀情」，今次的對象更是67歲的薛家燕！家燕媽媽日前出席活動接受傳媒訪問時，透露最近與吳業坤前往台灣工作，大爆對方對自己噓寒問暖，還直呼自己做「家燕」！同時她指吳業坤說夜晚到她的酒店房傾劇本，笑言怕對方太熱情，搞到夜晚都會鎖門！另外日前在《萬千星輝頒獎禮2017》上，薛家燕走紅地氈時不慎被長裙絆倒，吳業坤仲立即去扶「緋聞女友」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/213159_d9c571cb12d65330d701ba717415f511.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F213159_d9c571cb12d65330d701ba717415f511.png&h=062deb96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">影低家燕媽媽唇印</span><br />\n<br />\n直到昨日（22號），再有消息力證吳業坤「冧」家燕媽媽！同行去台灣的王梓軒昨日在社交網上傳影片，影片中王梓軒大爆遇到恐怖事件，就是吳業坤會經常Close up影低家燕媽媽飲水後留在水杯上的唇膏印，還指吳業坤影完相會講句「我的家燕寶寶」，至於問到薛家燕的感受，她就笑言受寵若驚，而王梓軒就加把口說：「佢（薛家燕）係受寵若『驚』，真心驚喎！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/213257_5f0e241efc596a14e09d3c83adebef2c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F213257_5f0e241efc596a14e09d3c83adebef2c.png&h=d8d90110&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cf6735bab65c873975f69243459f82cc5f74aa9","tid":837562,"uid":36702,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:34:40.000Z","msg":"有三粒lin可以啜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eca72e819cd17e7466edf3a449515224c5d4206","tid":837562,"uid":137831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cf6735bab65c873975f69243459f82cc5f74aa9","tid":837562,"uid":36702,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T13:34:40.000Z","msg":"有三粒lin可以啜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T23:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a427a368180d23bc18acbb6adfd059922704582c","tid":837562,"uid":4242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eca72e819cd17e7466edf3a449515224c5d4206","tid":837562,"uid":137831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cf6735bab65c873975f69243459f82cc5f74aa9","tid":837562,"uid":36702,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201